</use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oyn1665702570922.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oyn1665702570922.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oyn1665702570922.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oyn1665702570922\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__lfilerename_226695\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Rename a file in the same directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__topic_d74063e1_d74064e1_d74065e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__p_d74066e1_d74067e1_d74068e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfilerename</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FilePath</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NewFileName</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__section_w1666ab1b7b5_w1667ab1b7_w1668ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__p_d74069e1_d74070e1_d74071e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">lfilerename \"test.txt\", \"tested.txt\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__topic_d48787e1_d48788e1_d48789e1_d48790e1_d48791e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d202525e82\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FilePath</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20__entry__3\">File name, optionally preceded by the path\n\t\t\t\t to the file. Must not end with a directory separator.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">NewFileName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__d6138e20__entry__3\">New file name. Must not end with a directory separator and must not include the path to the file.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__topic_d48792e1_d48793e1_d48794e1_d48795e1_d48796e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d202525e151\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__2\">Error constant </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__3\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__2\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__3\">Successful</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-13</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UIOSERR_OS_COMMAND&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"oyn1665702570922__table_d6362e1_d6363e1_d6364e1__entry__3\">An error occurred while trying to perform the\n                     OS command. Set <code class=\"ph codeph\">/pri=64</code> to display the exact error in the\n                     message frame.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__topic_d48797e1_d48798e1_d48799e1_d48800e1_d48801e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d202525e238\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__topic_d48802e1_d48803e1_d48804e1_d48805e1_d48806e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d202525e247\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oyn1665702570922__p_d74087e1_d74088e1_d74089e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfilerename</span> statement renames <var class=\"keyword varname\">FilePath</var> to <var class=\"keyword varname\">NewFileName</var> within the same directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file. The file can be renamed in a ZIP archive. In other respects, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lfilerename</span> works the same as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">filerename</span>. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mrg1720023653521.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mrg1720023653521.html\" title=\"Rename a file in the same directory.\">filerename</a>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bau1719406118842.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ProcScript for File System Management</a><p>Uniface provides ProcScript statements and functions for managing local files and directories.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mrg1720023653521.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>filerename</a><p>Rename a file in the same directory.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wek1720014192425.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>dirrename</a><p>Rename the specified directory.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/evz1665702570697.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ldirrename</a><p>Rename the specified directory, ignoring redirections in the assignment file.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530804\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530804\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "lfilerename Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Rename a file in the same directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file. lfilerename FilePath , NewFileName Example: lfilerename \"test.txt\", \"tested.txt\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description FilePath String File name, optionally preceded by the path to the file. Must not end with a directory separator. NewFileName String New file name. Must not end with a directory separator and must not include the path to the file. Return Values Table 2. Values returned by $procerror Value Error constant Meaning 0 Successful -13 <UIOSERR_OS_COMMAND> An error occurred while trying to perform the OS command. Set /pri=64 to display the exact error in the message frame. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The lfilerename statement renames FilePath to NewFileName within the same directory, ignoring any file redirections in the assignment file. The file can be renamed in a ZIP archive. In other respects, lfilerename works the same as filerename . For more information, see filerename . Related Links ProcScript for File System Management Uniface provides ProcScript statements and functions for managing local files and directories. filerename Rename a file in the same directory. dirrename Rename the specified directory. ldirrename Rename the specified directory, ignoring redirections in the assignment file. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}